parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Tire tread separation can lead to loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries, especially when the tire comes off the rim and strikes other vehicles or objects.
symptoms: The tire tread separates from the sidewall
causing the tire to come off the rim
potentially striking other vehicles or objects
and leading to loss of vehicle control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Trailer tire failure can cause the tire to come off the trailer, leading to accidents, injuries, and damage to other vehicles or property.
symptoms: The trailer tire comes off the trailer
potentially striking other vehicles or objects
and leading to loss of vehicle control.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Axle Damage Causing Trailer Swaying and Loss of Control
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Axle damage can cause the trailer to sway, leading to loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle and trailer. This can result in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The trailer sways or wobbles while towing
the vehicle is difficult to control
the vehicle and trailer experience sudden movements or jerks
the axle or wheel components show signs of damage or wear.
